{"text_id":197068,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," novel"," model"," for"," learning"," to"," segment"," temporal"," sequences",","," which"," lever","ages"," a"," mixture"," of"," Recurrent"," Neural"," Network"," (","RNN",")"," experts"," coupled"," with"," adaptive"," variance","."," This"," approach"," aims"," to"," address"," the"," challenging"," problem"," of"," identifying"," meaningful"," segments"," within"," sequential"," data",","," where"," the"," number"," and"," boundaries"," of"," segments"," are"," unknown"," beforehand","."," Our"," model"," capital","izes"," on"," the"," strengths"," of"," multiple"," RNN"," experts",","," each"," trained"," to"," capture"," distinct"," patterns"," in"," the"," data",","," and"," adap","tively"," adjusts"," the"," variance"," of"," their"," predictions"," to"," better"," reflect"," uncertainty","."," This"," results"," in"," improved"," segmentation"," accuracy"," and"," robustness"," to"," diverse"," sequence"," lengths"," and"," structures","."," Our"," experimental"," results"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach"," on"," various"," benchmark"," datasets",","," out","performing"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," methods","."," We"," achieve"," significant"," improvements"," in"," segmentation"," quality",","," as"," measured"," by"," metrics"," such"," as"," precision",","," recall",","," and"," F","1","-","score","."," The"," key"," idea"," behind"," our"," model"," is"," to"," exploit"," the"," complementary"," strengths"," of"," multiple"," RNN"," experts"," and"," adap","tively"," modulate"," their"," influence"," based"," on"," the"," observed"," variance","."," By"," doing"," so",","," we"," provide"," a"," more"," accurate"," and"," flexible"," framework"," for"," learning"," to"," segment"," temporal"," sequences","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}